---
import Prose from "@components/Prose.astro";
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  pageTitle="Now | Hyun Don Moon"
  pageDescription="What I'm up to right now"
>
  <Prose>
    <h1>Now</h1>

    <p>
      This page is inspired by Derek Sivers' <a
        href="https://nownownow.com/about"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">/now pages</a
      > movement. It's a simple concept: a page that tells you what someone is focused
      on at this point in their life.
    </p>

    <section>
      <h3>July, 2025</h3>

      <h4>Learning</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Finished reading <em>The Pragmatic Programmer</em>, focusing on its lessons about DRY principles.</li>
        <li>Started the “Advanced TypeScript” course on Frontend Masters to deepen my skills.</li>
      </ul>

      <h4>Projects</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Refactored the Astro blog’s header component to add dark mode support.</li>
      </ul>

      <h4>Fitness</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Completed a 5K run in 25:30, setting a new personal best for the month.</li>
      </ul>

      <h4>Life</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Spent an afternoon exploring the traditional architecture at Bukchon Hanok Village.</li>
        <li>Perfected a new homemade ramen recipe.</li>
        <li>Caught up with a friend over dinner.</li>
        <li>Bought my first pair of Vans slip-ons.</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top:2em; font-size:0.9em; color: #666;">
        This page was updated automatically using n8n & Google Gemini.
      </p>
    </section>
  </Prose>
</BaseLayout>